<subSubSection id="F7D86578FFB01B07FE36FA51040A40EA" pageId="14" pageNumber="164" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="BF7D36F3FFB01B07FE36FA51037940E7" blockId="14.[429,1824,1303,2561]" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">
<location id="BA1D6028FFB01B07FE36FA51059F4038" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:376B87E5FFB01B07FE77FAA2040A40EA:BA1D6028FFB01B07FE36FA51059F4038" box="[492,665,1508,1550]" country="Northern Mariana Islands" county="July" municipality="From" name="Described" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">Described</location>
from 
<collectingCountry id="C7D57663FFB01B07FCCAFA5103424038" box="[784,1092,1508,1550]" name="Northern Mariana Islands" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">Marianas Islands</collectingCountry>
, and not recorded elsewhere. 
<location id="BA1D6028FFB01B07F9BBFA5101A94038" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:376B87E5FFB01B07FE77FAA2040A40EA:BA1D6028FFB01B07F9BBFA5101A94038" box="[1633,1711,1508,1550]" country="Northern Mariana Islands" county="July" municipality="From" name="This" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">This</location>
abundant green species is smaller and duller. 
<location id="BA1D6028FFB01B07FB59F9A303CE4077" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:376B87E5FFB01B07FE77FAA2040A40EA:BA1D6028FFB01B07FB59F9A303CE4077" box="[1155,1224,1558,1601]" country="Northern Mariana Islands" county="July" municipality="From" name="The" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">The</location>
larvae were found very abundant under bark of remaining top of an 
<taxonomicName id="78C24D70FFB01B07FBFAF9F902054042" authorityName=", Swezey. E. C." box="[1056,1283,1612,1652]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Intsia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="14" pageNumber="164" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bijuga">
<emphasis id="8DB6EAE1FFB01B07FBFAF9F902054042" box="[1056,1283,1612,1652]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">Intsia bijuga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
tree which had been cut off at 
<location id="BA1D6028FFB01B07FE74F9CB05584091" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:376B87E5FFB01B07FE77FAA2040A40EA:BA1D6028FFB01B07FE74F9CB05584091" box="[430,606,1662,1703]" country="Northern Mariana Islands" county="July" municipality="From" name="Barrigacla" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">Barrigacla</location>
for timber. 
<collectingMunicipality id="5F19AC89FFB01B07FC93F9CB04AD4091" box="[841,939,1662,1703]" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">From</collectingMunicipality>
portion of branch, taken home 
<collectingCounty id="561C4E7FFFB01B07FA3CF9CB01374091" box="[1510,1585,1662,1703]" pageId="14" pageNumber="164">July</collectingCounty>
22, 
<specimenCount id="A9C4FD7AFFB01B07F95FF9CB00264091" box="[1669,1824,1662,1703]" pageId="14" pageNumber="164" type="adult">10 adults</specimenCount>
issued between August 3 and October 1.
</paragraph>
